<section id="howSection">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>From PDF to online test in four simple steps.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="how-section">
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <h3>Upload Your Paper</h3>
        <p>Open the Test Generator and upload your reading passage, question paper, and answer key as PDFs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <h3>AI Extracts Content</h3>
        <p>Gemini AI reads your documents and pulls out passages, questions, options, and correct answers automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <h3>Review &amp; Generate</h3>
        <p>Check the extracted content, fix anything that needs tweaking, then download the finished test as an HTML file.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <h3>Share &amp; Analyse</h3>
        <p>Upload the test to GitHub Pages and share the link. Results flow to your Google Sheet for analysis.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
